{"tid":598984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林行止：特朗普蓬佩奧並肩劍指中國　中美關係進入高危期","createTime":"2018-03-20T04:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T13:30:14.000Z","uid":56015,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b79c3d3b7be4801e6f81a363a1f6028aaf40a412","tid":598984,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T04:28:58.000Z","msg":"2018-3-20 12:22<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普上任以來，白宮時有人事變動。《信報》創辦人林行止於今日該報專欄指出，白宮決策層已人面全非，總統助理、經濟顧問以至國務卿人選都是「仇中派」，意味國防部長及國安顧問會否換人，美國的對華政策也只會日趨強橫，「中美關係已進入高危期」。<br />\n<br />\n蒂勒森擔任國務卿時期，不時與特朗普意見相左。林行止指出，在外交事務上，如果兩人看法有分歧，而總統不聽國務卿意見，美國的外交政策將予人「吹無定向風左搖右擺」之感，其他國家領袖也不敢對美國的外交主張照單全收，亦即西方國家在國際舞台上會變得群龍無首，「讓敵對陣營有機可乘」。相反，若特朗普與候任國務卿蓬佩奧「同鼻孔出氣」，美國在國際舞台上的影響力定會勝過蒂勒森時期。<br />\n<br />\n林行止形容，長期在商界工作的蒂勒森傾向「凡事有商有量」，屬溫和中庸派，沒有大幅改動與人為善的美國傳統外交總路線。蓬佩奧的外交手段則較為強硬，相信與會與特朗普並肩「作戰」，將矛頭直指中國。蓬佩奧在俄羅斯問題上態度較曖昧，但北京與伊朗事務方面與特朗普取態一致。林行止稱，如國會通過蓬佩奧的任命，「世界愈來愈亂，不難預期」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/245426/%e6%9e%97%e8%a1%8c%e6%ad%a2%ef%bc%9a%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e8%93%ac%e4%bd%a9%e5%a5%a7%e4%b8%a6%e8%82%a9%e5%8a%8d%e6%8c%87%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e3%80%80%e4%b8%ad%e7%be%8e%e9%97%9c%e4%bf%82%e9%80%b2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F245426%2F%25e6%259e%2597%25e8%25a1%258c%25e6%25ad%25a2%25ef%25bc%259a%25e7%2589%25b9%25e6%259c%2597%25e6%2599%25ae%25e8%2593%25ac%25e4%25bd%25a9%25e5%25a5%25a7%25e4%25b8%25a6%25e8%2582%25a9%25e5%258a%258d%25e6%258c%2587%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e3%2580%2580%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e7%25be%258e%25e9%2597%259c%25e4%25bf%2582%25e9%2580%25b2%2F&d=D%2BverwI54%2FCFhfeffaWAvghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=22f42c0d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/245426/%e6%9e%97%e8%a1%8c%e6%ad%a2%ef%bc%9a%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e8%93%ac%e4%bd%a9%e5%a5%a7%e4%b8%a6%e8%82%a9%e5%8a%8d%e6%8c%87%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e3%80%80%e4%b8%ad%e7%be%8e%e9%97%9c%e4%bf%82%e9%80%b2/</a>"},{"pid":"878502634d7b633702e417fe35ba5c84e8b70255","tid":598984,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T04:30:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林銀止瀨共狗，852含林鳩！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3b064dafabda505853f9e7e29782c452700ea618","tid":598984,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T04:53:16.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec73c4b7c3f92d5e7fd4f30077904f98aaab87c","tid":598984,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T04:54:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲論調同五毛既，最衰美國搞亂世界，有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac592627097bb9a530c70b8ade0e10251f45fdca","tid":598984,"uid":37735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T04:56:33.000Z","msg":"班5毛 同 強國 仲打飛機<br />\n<br />\n人地扮野<br />\n<br />\n過完台灣關係法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add3c2e8950d2471f4815d4b96efd46a6b3a0b1f","tid":598984,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:10:39.000Z","msg":"上次美國新任命駐澳洲大使，支那日報係度嘈嘈嘈<br />\n今次換副總統係咪又要嘈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n干涉別國內政專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0f56e23a7452cf36925bf0a5a8e3e4cae1b65d","tid":598984,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:59:30.000Z","msg":"又係人攪衰你<br />\n永遠唔係自己攪衰自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510fe1610c1b465de3f95f876d319d5b29cb6c7d","tid":598984,"uid":21028,"like":0,"disl